question.text: A loop <math><mi mathvariant="normal">A</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">B</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">C</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">D</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">E</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">F</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">A</mi></math> of straight edges has six corner points <math><mi>A</mi><mfenced separators="|"><mrow><mn>0</mn><mo>,</mo><mi></mi><mn>0</mn><mo>,</mo><mi></mi><mn>0</mn></mrow></mfenced><mo>,</mo><mi></mi><mi>B</mi><mfenced separators="|"><mrow><mn>5</mn><mo>,</mo><mi></mi><mn>0</mn><mo>,</mo><mi></mi><mn>0</mn></mrow></mfenced><mo>,</mo><mi></mi><mi>C</mi><mfenced separators="|"><mrow><mn>5</mn><mo>,</mo><mi></mi><mn>5</mn><mo>,</mo><mi></mi><mn>0</mn></mrow></mfenced><mo>,</mo><mi></mi><mi>D</mi><mfenced separators="|"><mrow><mn>0</mn><mo>,</mo><mi></mi><mn>5</mn><mo>,</mo><mi></mi><mn>0</mn></mrow></mfenced><mo>,</mo><mi></mi><mi>E</mi><mfenced separators="|"><mrow><mn>0</mn><mo>,</mo><mi></mi><mn>5</mn><mo>,</mo><mi></mi><mn>5</mn></mrow></mfenced></math> and <math><mi>F</mi><mfenced separators="|"><mrow><mn>0</mn><mo>,</mo><mi></mi><mn>0</mn><mo>,</mo><mi></mi><mn>5</mn></mrow></mfenced></math> . The magnetic field in this region is <math><mover accent="true"><mrow><mi>B</mi></mrow><mo>→</mo></mover><mo>=</mo><mfenced separators="|"><mrow><mn>3</mn><mover accent="true"><mrow><mi>i</mi></mrow><mo>^</mo></mover><mo>+</mo><mn>4</mn><mover accent="true"><mrow><mi>k</mi></mrow><mo>^</mo></mover></mrow></mfenced><mi>T</mi></math> . The quantity of flux through the loop <math><mi mathvariant="normal">A</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">B</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">C</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">D</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">E</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">F</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">A</mi></math> (in <math><mi mathvariant="normal">W</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">b</mi></math> ) is _____________
